<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Vamshikrishna Kamboja | SAP FICO & Accounts Payable Specialist</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0a1628;
    --deep: #0d1f3c;
    --gold: #c9a84c;
    --gold-light: #e8c97a;
    --cream: #f5f0e8;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --text-muted: #8a9ab5;
    --card-bg: #111e35;
    --border: rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ─── NAV ─── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100;
    padding: 1.2rem 4rem;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    background: rgba(10,22,40,0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    text-decoration: none; color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  #hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex; align-items: center;
    padding: 6rem 4rem 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 80% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.07) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 60% at 10% 80%, rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }

  .hero-grid {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0.04;
    background-image: 
      linear-gradient(var(--gold) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
  }

  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 800px; }

  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--white);
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.15s ease both;
  }

  .hero-name span { color: var(--gold); }

  .hero-role {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.3s ease both;
  }

  .hero-role strong { color: var(--cream); font-weight: 500; }

  .hero-cta {
    margin-top: 3rem; display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.45s ease both;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy);
    padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border: none; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .btn-outline {
    border: 1px solid var(--gold); color: var(--gold);
    padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;
    transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute; bottom: 2.5rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center;
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
  }
  .hero-scroll::after {
    content: ''; display: block; width: 1px; height: 50px;
    background: var(--gold); margin: 0.5rem auto 0;
  }

  /* ─── SECTIONS ─── */
  section { padding: 6rem 4rem; }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  /* ─── ABOUT ─── */
  #about { background: var(--deep); }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.9; color: #b0bdd4; }
  .about-text p { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.8rem;
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.03);
    transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
  }
  .stat-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold); transform: translateY(-3px); }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700;
  }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.3rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

  /* ─── SKILLS ─── */
  #skills {}

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skill-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }

  .skill-card::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 3px; height: 0; background: var(--gold);
    transition: height 0.4s;
  }
  .skill-card:hover::before { height: 100%; }
  .skill-card:hover { border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.5); transform: translateY(-4px); }

  .skill-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .skill-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .skill-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; margin-top: 1rem; }

  .tag {
    font-size: 0.72rem; padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
    color: var(--gold-light); letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.05);
  }

  /* ─── TRAINING ─── */
  #training { background: var(--deep); }

  .training-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 3rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr; gap: 3rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .training-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }

  .training-meta { border-right: 1px solid var(--border); padding-right: 3rem; }

  .training-period {
    font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .training-org { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  .training-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .modules-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.6rem; }

  .module-item {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem; color: #9aabca; line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .module-item::before { content: '◆'; color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.5rem; margin-top: 0.35rem; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* ─── EXPERIENCE ─── */
  #experience {}

  .exp-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .exp-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }

  .exp-header {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;
  }

  .exp-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--white);
  }

  .exp-company { color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.3rem; }

  .exp-period {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .exp-points { list-style: none; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.8rem; }

  .exp-points li {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.88rem; color: #9aabca; line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .exp-points li::before { content: '→'; color: var(--gold); flex-shrink: 0; }

  .transition-note {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.05);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ─── CONTACT ─── */
  #contact { background: var(--deep); text-align: center; }

  .contact-inner { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 3rem; text-align: left;
  }

  .contact-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .contact-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }

  .contact-card-label { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .contact-card-value { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--cream); word-break: break-all; }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    text-align: center; padding: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* ─── ANIMATIONS ─── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(8px); }
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    #hero { padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .about-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .training-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .training-meta { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-right: 0; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .modules-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .exp-points { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">VK</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
    <li><a href="#training">Training</a></li>
    <li><a href="#experience">Experience</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-tag">Open to Opportunities</div>
    <h1 class="hero-name">Vamshi<span>krishna</span><br>Kamboja</h1>
    <p class="hero-role">
      <strong>SAP FICO End User (Trained)</strong> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
      <strong>Accounts Payable & P2P Specialist</strong><br>
      Transitioning from GIS Operations into Finance & ERP — combining 2+ years of corporate discipline with hands-on SAP FICO training.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Get In Touch</a>
      <a href="#skills" class="btn-outline">View Skills</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">Scroll</div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="section-label">Who I Am</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Finance Professional<br>in the Making</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="about-grid reveal">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>A B.Com graduate and SAP FICO End User trained professional, I bring over 2 years of structured corporate experience at Movate Pvt. Ltd., where I built strong foundations in data accuracy, SOP adherence, and cross-functional collaboration.</p>
      <p>Having completed comprehensive SAP FICO training at My ERP Hub, Hyderabad (July 2025), I am now channelling my analytical mindset and process discipline into a focused career in Accounts Payable and ERP operations.</p>
      <p>My journey from GIS data quality to finance is powered by one consistent strength: the ability to verify, reconcile, and validate complex information — precisely what Accounts Payable demands.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-stats">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">2+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Years Corporate Experience</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">SAP</div>
        <div class="stat-label">FICO End User Certified</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">P2P</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Full Cycle Knowledge</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">B.Com</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Osmania University, 2021</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SKILLS -->
<section id="skills">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="section-label">Core Competencies</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Skills & Expertise</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="skills-grid">
    <div class="skill-card reveal">
      <div class="skill-icon">📊</div>
      <div class="skill-title">SAP FICO</div>
      <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#8a9ab5;line-height:1.6;">Hands-on SAP ECC 6.0 & S/4HANA training covering GL, AP, AR modules with real-world process simulations.</p>
      <div class="skill-tags">
        <span class="tag">SAP ECC 6.0</span>
        <span class="tag">S/4HANA</span>
        <span class="tag">F-53</span>
        <span class="tag">APP</span>
        <span class="tag">GL Accounting</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-card reveal">
      <div class="skill-icon">🔄</div>
      <div class="skill-title">P2P Cycle</div>
      <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#8a9ab5;line-height:1.6;">End-to-end Procure-to-Pay process knowledge from Purchase Requisition through to Vendor Payment.</p>
      <div class="skill-tags">
        <span class="tag">PR → PO</span>
        <span class="tag">GRN</span>
        <span class="tag">3-Way Match</span>
        <span class="tag">2-Way Match</span>
        <span class="tag">Invoice Posting</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-card reveal">
      <div class="skill-icon">🧾</div>
      <div class="skill-title">Invoice Processing</div>
      <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#8a9ab5;line-height:1.6;">Comprehensive experience in verifying PO, Non-PO, and Service invoices with GST/tax validation.</p>
      <div class="skill-tags">
        <span class="tag">PO Invoices</span>
        <span class="tag">Non-PO Invoices</span>
        <span class="tag">GST Validation</span>
        <span class="tag">Duplicate Detection</span>
        <span class="tag">Debit/Credit Memos</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-card reveal">
      <div class="skill-icon">🤝</div>
      <div class="skill-title">Vendor Management</div>
      <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#8a9ab5;line-height:1.6;">Vendor master data creation, reconciliation, and query resolution to maintain strong vendor relationships.</p>
      <div class="skill-tags">
        <span class="tag">Master Data</span>
        <span class="tag">Reconciliation</span>
        <span class="tag">Payment Terms</span>
        <span class="tag">Banking Details</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-card reveal">
      <div class="skill-icon">📅</div>
      <div class="skill-title">Month-End Closing</div>
      <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#8a9ab5;line-height:1.6;">GR/IR reconciliation, AP aging reports, open item clearing, and balance carryforward within deadlines.</p>
      <div class="skill-tags">
        <span class="tag">GR/IR Reconciliation</span>
        <span class="tag">AP Aging</span>
        <span class="tag">Open Item Clearing</span>
        <span class="tag">Ledger Recon</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-card reveal">
      <div class="skill-icon">💻</div>
      <div class="skill-title">Tools & Compliance</div>
      <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#8a9ab5;line-height:1.6;">Proficient in MS Excel for financial analysis and committed to SOP adherence and audit support.</p>
      <div class="skill-tags">
        <span class="tag">Excel (VLOOKUP)</span>
        <span class="tag">Pivot Tables</span>
        <span class="tag">Audit Support</span>
        <span class="tag">SOP Adherence</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TRAINING -->
<section id="training">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="section-label">Education & Training</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Professional Development</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="training-card reveal">
    <div class="training-meta">
      <div class="training-period">July 2025</div>
      <div class="training-org">My ERP Hub<br>KPHB, Hyderabad</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="training-title">SAP FICO End User Training</div>
      <div class="modules-grid">
        <div class="module-item">Financial Accounting (FI): GL, AP, AR</div>
        <div class="module-item">Controlling (CO): Cost Centers, Internal Orders</div>
        <div class="module-item">End-to-End P2P Cycle (PR→PO→GRN→Payment)</div>
        <div class="module-item">Vendor Master Data & Payment Terms</div>
        <div class="module-item">Payment Execution via F-53 & APP Runs</div>
        <div class="module-item">2-Way & 3-Way Invoice Matching</div>
        <div class="module-item">Debit/Credit Memo Processing</div>
        <div class="module-item">Month-End: GR/IR Reconciliation & Closing</div>
        <div class="module-item">Document Parking, Holding & Reversals</div>
        <div class="module-item">Accrual Postings & GL Line-Item Analysis</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="training-card reveal">
    <div class="training-meta">
      <div class="training-period">2021</div>
      <div class="training-org">Osmania University<br>Hyderabad</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="training-title">Bachelor of Commerce (B.Com)</div>
      <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#9aabca;line-height:1.7;">Strong foundation in accounting principles, financial management, business law, and commerce — directly aligned with AP and finance operations requirements.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EXPERIENCE -->
<section id="experience">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="section-label">Work History</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Professional Experience</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="exp-card reveal">
    <div class="exp-header">
      <div>
        <div class="exp-title">GIS Data Quality Executive</div>
        <div class="exp-company">Movate Pvt. Ltd.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-period">May 2022 – April 2025</div>
    </div>
    <ul class="exp-points">
      <li>Verified and validated large volumes of business data (POI) against multiple sources — mirroring 3-way invoice matching</li>
      <li>Maintained meticulous documentation and audit logs for all data changes, building habits aligned with AP compliance</li>
      <li>Collaborated with cross-functional teams to resolve discrepancies and meet project milestones</li>
      <li>Applied structured quality-check frameworks and SOPs to meet accuracy and productivity benchmarks</li>
      <li>Managed multiple concurrent tasks and consistently delivered within deadlines across rotational shifts</li>
      <li>Developed strong data accuracy discipline directly transferable to vendor invoice validation workflows</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="transition-note">
      <strong style="color:var(--gold);">Career Transition Note:</strong> Skills developed in GIS operations — data verification, cross-referencing, SOP adherence, documentation, and cross-team collaboration — are directly transferable to Accounts Payable and SAP FICO operations.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTACT -->
<section id="contact">
  <div class="reveal contact-inner">
    <p class="section-label">Let's Connect</p>
    <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Open to AP &<br>SAP FICO Roles</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.8;">Actively seeking entry-level SAP FICO End User or AP Executive positions in Hyderabad. Ready to apply both corporate discipline and newly acquired ERP skills from day one.</p>
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="contact-card-label">Email</div>
        <div class="contact-card-value">kambojavamshikrishna@gmail.com</div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="contact-card-label">Phone</div>
        <div class="contact-card-value">+91 8790688496</div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="contact-card-label">Location</div>
        <div class="contact-card-value">Hyderabad, Telangana, India</div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="contact-card-label">Availability</div>
        <div class="contact-card-value">Immediately Available</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2025 Vamshikrishna Kamboja &nbsp;·&nbsp; SAP FICO & Accounts Payable Specialist</p>
</footer>

<script>
  // Scroll reveal
  const reveals = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach((entry, i) => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        setTimeout(() => entry.target.classList.add('visible'), i * 80);
        observer.unobserve(entry.target);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.1 });
  reveals.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>
</body>
</html>
